If you think you have stress - related problems on the job , there 's good news and bad news .
You 're probably right , and you are n't alone .
<COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">A new Gallup Poll study commissioned by <COREF ID="13" TYPE="IDENT">the New York Business Group on Health</COREF></COREF> , found that a full 25 % of the work force at companies may suffer from <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">anxiety disorders or a stress - related illness</COREF> , with about 13 % suffering from depression .
