<COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">It</COREF> is one of a series of studies on health commissioned by <COREF ID="13" TYPE="IDENT">the New York Business Group , a non-profit organization with about 300 members</COREF> .
<COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">The stress study</COREF> was undertaken because <COREF ID="11" TYPE="IDENT">problems related to stress</COREF> `` are much more prevalent than <COREF ID="11" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> seem , '' said <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">Leon J. Warshaw , executive director of <COREF ID="13" TYPE="IDENT">the business group</COREF></COREF> .
